00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:18.000
We're going to publish it to Posit Connect and share it with everyone here on the line.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:22.000
So we're going to primarily live within Workbench and Connect today.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:24.000
And then we'll touch upon Package Manager.

